      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 53.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 53.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>使我介然有知，行於大道，唯施是畏。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>If I were suddenly to become known, and (put into a position to) conduct (a government) according to the Great Dao, what I should be most afraid of would be a boastful display.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-053__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-053</prop>
