      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 53.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 53.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>服文綵，帶利劍，厭飲食，財貨有餘；是為盜夸。非道也哉！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>This is contrary to the Dao surely!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
